OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly patches of low cloud and
OL,6,Ffog will readily clear during the
OL,7,Fmorning to leave a dry day across the
OL,8,Fregion with some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Feeling very warm in the light
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain dry overnight
OL,13,Fwith variable cloud. There will be
OL,14,Fsome clear spells, though patches of
OL,15,Flow cloud and fog are likely to reform
OL,16,Fby the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
